      "text": "いや、話くらい最後まで聞いて下さいよ……",
      "startTime": 18.2666673978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんもスリクスを結成する前に……\nSundanceとしてグランプリで優勝してますよね",
      "startTime": 24.3666673978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……私の前のグループをご存じだったんですね",
      "startTime": 27.9000020027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ知ってますよ。俺はマネージャーですよ",
      "startTime": 31.3333362262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（Sundanceは、藤代葉さんとの二人組で）\n（BIG4にも迫ろうかという人気ユニットだった）",
      "startTime": 38.633338515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（しかし人気絶頂期に活動休止）\n（その後、mihoさんはⅢXを結成したわけだが……）",
      "startTime": 45.4000036557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……昔のことですよ",
      "startTime": 49.9666693051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "どうでしょう、先方もmihoさんに\nぜひ出てほしいとおっしゃってますし",
      "startTime": 54.6000036556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "お断りします\n今、スリクスは新曲リリースの準備で忙しいんです",
      "startTime": 58.6666749,
